products.title: Intel Core i7-8086K Desktop Processor 6 Cores up to 5.0 GHz unlocked LGA 1151 300 Series 95W
features: 4.00 GHz up to 5.00 GHz Max Turbo Frequency / 12 MB Cache
Compatible only with Motherboards based on Intel 300 Series Chipsets
products.description: In celebration of the 40th Anniversary of Intel's first 8086 microprocessor. 8th Gen Intel Core i7-8086K Limited Edition unlocked processor, best of 8th Gen desktop processor family capabilities with HIGHER frequency. First up to 5.0 GHz consumer processor. Commemorative packaging. Limited availability. ONLY compatible with Intel 300 Series chipset based motherboard. Thermal solution NOT included in the box.
